  <brief_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of Exercise Training Among Men With Type 2-diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of Strength Versus Aerobic Exercise Training to Improve Glycemic Control in Men With Type 2-diabetes</official_title>
