  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosed with type 2-diabetes

          -  Male, 35-71 years

          -  Managing their diabetes through a lifestyle and/or the drug metformin only

          -  Able to participate in either of the exercise groups

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Symptomatic cardiovascular disease

          -  Uncontrolled hypertension

          -  Physical or cognitive disabilities that will interfere with participating in the
             exercise regimes.

          -  Trained consistently during the last six months.
